node.text:
Welcome to paradise with @adrianbaias and @florina__toma at Calilo, a tranquil retreat - a visionary conservation project that offers an escape from the clamour and the crowds. Think sun-drenched seclusion surrounded by an ancient olive-pricked landscape - @nature and art at its heart. Find yourself and all you need in a land in deep connection with everything.

Who would you share this hideout with? 😌

📽 @adrianbaias w/ @florina__toma #nature
📍 Calilo Hotel, Ios, Greece
🎶 Henry Mancini - Lujon
